===NES version===

The game was later ported to the [[Nintendo Entertainment System]] (NES) and [[Famicom Disk System|Family Computer Disk System]] (FDS) in 1988. The game has a new storyline: In 1849, a [[gang]] known as the Wingates attacks the town of Hicksville, kills the sheriff, and causes trouble everyday until Billie Bob, the main character, comes to town to free it from the gang. The NES version also has different music.

==Soundtrack==
